&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10.5pt;"&gt;No total, serão apresentadas 8 palestras:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10.5pt;"&gt;- Datacenter Celepar: gestão em ambiente em SL;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
