&lt;p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10.5pt;"&gt;Veja a programação completa &lt;a href="http://www.circuito.pr.gov.br/arquivos/File/programacao_06.pdf" target="_blank"&gt;aqui: http://www.circuito.pr.gov.br/arquivos/File/programacao_06.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
